# Example MTL file

newmtl MaterialName
Ka 1.000 1.000 1.000  # Ambient color (white)
Kd 1.000 1.000 1.000  # Diffuse color (white)
Ks 0.000 0.000 0.000  # Specular color (black)
Ns 10.0               # Shininess
d 1.0                 # Transparency (1.0 is fully opaque)
illum 2               # Illumination model (2 for diffuse and specular)

